# ============================================================================
# CODEOWNERS - Balancing Rock Project Template
# ============================================================================
# This file defines code ownership for automatic review assignment.
# Owners are automatically requested for review when someone opens a PR
# that modifies files they own.
#
# IMPORTANT: Update @YOUR-USERNAME with your actual GitHub username
# ============================================================================

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DEFAULT OWNER - Catches everything not matched below
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The owner(s) below will be the default owners for everything in the repo.
# Unless a later match takes precedence, these owners will be requested for
# review when someone opens a pull request.

*                                   @YOUR-USERNAME

