# ============================================================================
# TEAM EXPANSION TEMPLATE
# ============================================================================
# When you add team members, create team-based ownership:
#
# 1. Create GitHub Teams in your organization:
#    - @org/core-maintainers
#    - @org/backend-team
#    - @org/frontend-team
#    - @org/devops-team
#
# 2. Replace @YOUR-USERNAME with team references:
#    *                              @org/core-maintainers
#    /src/api/                      @org/backend-team
#    /src/frontend/                 @org/frontend-team
#    /.github/                      @org/devops-team
#
# 3. For AI agents, create a team and add their GitHub App:
#    /src/                          @org/ai-agents @org/core-maintainers
